sub_title: Partnerships UK at Savings United GmbH
summary: Hi, my name is Marianna, I come from Poland, but have gained international experiences by living in many other countries like the Netherlands, Germany, Austria, and Spain for various educational and job possibilities. Recently I have obtained my master's degree in Marketing in Krems, Austria. Currently I am working full-time at Savings United as Junior Partnerships Manager for Team UK.
